### Create Triangle Bar Shape Component - Recharts

Source: https://github.com/recharts/recharts/blob/main/storybook/stories/Customise.mdx

Renders custom triangle-shaped bars using SVG path elements. Destructures fill, x, y, width, height from props and generates path using getPath utility function. Enables non-rectangular bar visualizations in Recharts.

```javascript
export const TriangleBar = (...args) => {
  const {
    fill, x, y, width, height,
  } = args[0];

  return <path d={getPath(x, y, width, height)} stroke="none" fill={fill} />;
};
```

